&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>預設帳密veeam / veeam ,登入後進行修改
&lt;img src="https://kenkenny.synology.me:5543/images/2023/09/Change_Password.png"
loading="lazy"
alt="image-20230218152751705"
